  <revision rev="3" vrev="1">
    <srcmd5>ee6cc35c39069ff6394067754e3f6fff</srcmd5>
    <version>0.6.0</version>
    <time>1784307254</time>
    <user>dimstar_suse</user>
    <comment>- Update to version 0.6.0:
  * Add subcommand `branch show-base` (#118)
  * Implement forge pr view for current branch (#109)
  * Bump golang.org/x/crypto from 0.52.0 to 0.53.0 (#123)
  * Fix pr checkout for agit-based workflows in forgejo (#117)
  * Add custom helptext when --json is used (#110)
  * Add FORGEJO_TOKEN environment variable support (#116)
  * When viewing a pipeline, print the corresponding job ids (#108)
  * Support URLs in forge pr checkout (#104)
  * Add git_protocol setting to defaults and per-domain configs
    (#103)
  * Support dest and gitflags in `forge repo clone` (#101)
  * Normalize gitlabs opened and open states in issues and
    milestones (#85)
  * Initial implementation of PR checkout (#97)</comment>
    <requestid>1366428</requestid>
  </revision>
